			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I'm against the idea of a multitrigger clicklink.
<br />
One link at a time it's enough, safe.
<br />

<br />
But one feature i would like to see from funcom, is an auto-open link option. When this option would be ticked in F10 - chat, every link sent to you will autopopinto the current active info window. This way you may have a real conversation with your bot without the need to always click on a chat answer to advance. 
<br />

<br />
To avoid any annoyance, the links should autoopen only if a window is opened yet. I mean i dont want an autopopup but more an autopopinto.
<br />

<br />
Anyway if you are interested by the idea, we could suggest this feature to Funcom, and ask for a slider instead of an option to tick.
<br />

<br />
